---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import List from "@components/List.astro";
import Paragraph from "@components/Paragraph.astro";
import Section from "@components/Section.astro";
import ListItem from "@components/ListItem.astro";
---

<Section id="experience">
  <div class="space-y-1 sm:space-y-2">
    <Paragraph>
      As a leader, I've directed product teams with strong conviction, created
      design processes that embrace reality, and shipped revenue-generating
      products based on customer and market discovery.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph class="!indent-4">
      As a designer, I've crafted user interfaces that are as delightful as they
      are functional, improved positioning and drove better conversion through
      research, analytics and experimentation.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph class="!indent-4">
      Regardless of the role, I've consistently worn multiple hats—usually out
      of necessity, other times for the joy of building. It’s from these
      experiences that I've developed the following four principles.
    </Paragraph>
  </div>
  <List class="grid grid-cols-2 grid-rows-2 gap-4">
    <ListItem
      class="flex aspect-square -rotate-1 cursor-pointer rounded-2xl bg-emerald-100 p-2 transition-transform duration-300 hover:rotate-1"
    >
      <div
        class="flex aspect-square flex-col justify-between rounded-lg bg-emerald-200 p-6"
      >
        <Icon
          name="component"
          shape-rendering="geometricPrecision"
          class="h-8 w-8 text-zinc-950"
        />
        <Paragraph class="!text-lg !leading-snug">
          Polished designs are no good if they can't be found.
        </Paragraph>
      </div>
    </ListItem>
    <ListItem
      class="flex aspect-square rotate-1 cursor-pointer rounded-2xl bg-fuchsia-100 p-2 transition-transform duration-300 hover:-rotate-1"
    >
      <div
        class="flex aspect-square flex-col justify-between rounded-lg bg-fuchsia-200 p-6"
      >
        <Icon
          name="puzzle-piece"
          shape-rendering="geometricPrecision"
          class="h-8 w-8 text-zinc-950"
        />
        <Paragraph class="!text-lg !leading-snug">
          Customers set the course, but data shows the way.
        </Paragraph>
      </div>
    </ListItem>
    <ListItem
      class="flex aspect-square rotate-1 cursor-pointer rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 p-2 transition-transform duration-300 hover:-rotate-1"
    >
      <div
        class="flex aspect-square flex-col justify-between rounded-lg bg-amber-200 p-6"
      >
        <Icon
          name="hamburger"
          shape-rendering="geometricPrecision"
          class="h-8 w-8 text-zinc-950"
        />
        <Paragraph class="!text-lg !leading-snug">
          Brands are defined by their stories, not their logo.
        </Paragraph>
      </div>
    </ListItem>
    <ListItem
      class="flex aspect-square -rotate-1 cursor-pointer rounded-2xl bg-red-100 p-2 transition-transform duration-300 hover:rotate-1"
    >
      <div
        class="flex aspect-square flex-col justify-between rounded-lg bg-red-200 p-6"
      >
        <Icon
          name="chart-line"
          shape-rendering="geometricPrecision"
          class="h-8 w-8 text-zinc-950"
        />
        <Paragraph class="!text-lg !leading-snug">
          Revenue is the primary metric for measuring value.
        </Paragraph>
      </div>
    </ListItem>
  </List>
</Section>
